O 1948]"], "description": ["Weekly Ceased 10 Settembre 1948. Suspended Mar. 1, 1924; resumed Apr. 19, 1924. Available on microfilm from Library of Congress, Photoduplication Service, and Connecticut State Library. Text in Italian and English. Description based on: Anno. VII, No. 15 (April 17, 1920); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 1, 2019). Latest issue consulted: Anno XVII, No. 51 (20 Dicembre 1930) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed May 1, 2019)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:47.120Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2019271083/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["italian", "english"], "location": ["fairfield", "bridgeport", "connecticut", "fairfield county", "united states"], "number": ["2019271083", "online resource", "1099570284", "2643-5101", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Sentinel"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "la sentinella = the sentinel (bridgeport, conn.) 191?-1948 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 79.62514, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["bridgeport", "fairfield", "connecticut", "newspapers", "italian", "fairfield county (conn.)", "bridgeport (conn.)", "italians", "fairfield county", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:58:32.070Z", "title": "La sentinella = The sentinel", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2019271083/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2015218855/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1803", "dates": ["[1803 TO 1929]"], "description": ["Weekly Began November 16, 1803. Published in Danbury, Conn., <November 16, 1803->;Bridgeport, Conn. <May 23, 1810->. Publishers: T. Rowe & Co., <November 16, 1803->; Stiles Nichols & Son <July 12, 1815->. Issues for <May 9, 1843-July 19, 1861> called also <new ser., v. 2, no. 71-new ser., v. 19, no. 1020>. Daily eds.: Daily advertiser and farmer, Sept. 8, 1856-186, and: Evening farmer, 186 -18, and: Bridgeport evening farmer, 18 -1917, and: Bridgeport times and evening farmer, 1918-192. New series vol. CXVII, no. 5107 (title from masthead) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed September 23, 2015). New series vol. CXXVIII, no. 5729 (August 13, 1920) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed September 23, 2015)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:03.421Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2015218855/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["fairfield", "bridgeport", "danbury", "connecticut", "fairfield county", "united states"], "number": ["192107503", "2015218853", "online resource", "2381-0114", "2015218855", "2015218854", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Issues for <Aug. 12, 1864-Feb. 1865> published as: Bridgeport Republican farmer", "Issue for <Aug. 24, 1866> published as: Weekly Republican farmer", "Issue for <May 21, 1897> published as: Weekly farmer"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "republican farmer (bridgeport, conn.) 1803-192? [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 66.91799, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD AN1 .A15", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["bridgeport", "fairfield", "danbury", "danbury (conn.)", "connecticut", "newspapers", "agricultural newspapers", "fairfield county (conn.)", "bridgeport (conn.)", "fairfield county", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:52:06.072Z", "title": "Republican farmer", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2015218855/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://infoweb.newsbank.com/?db=EANX&s_browseRef=decades/14DE99CA2A23A1A6/all.xml",